		<text style="width: 924px;margin-bottom:0px"><![CDATA[但小江並未察覺到賄賂的警訊......]]></text>
	</contentText>
	<contentBackground>
		<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c01/m10c01s10/contentBackground.jpg" minwidth="769"><![CDATA[小江正在廚房裡跟諾倫講電話]]></img>
